es to get a straight job, but the temptation to steal is hard to resist.","genre_ids":[80,18],"popularity":3.071,"vote_count":553,"poster_path":"/kxpvceDv9fhFc4OAs82fmdzu17Y.jpg","release_date":"1959-12-16","vote_average":7.271,"backdrop_path":"/5ApVROxPul7vu9NiB2DJWqlA3kE.jpg","original_title":"Pickpocket","original_language":"fr"},{"id":694,"adult":false,"title":"The Shining","video":false,"overview":"Jack Torrance accepts a caretaker job at the Overlook Hotel, where he, along with his wife Wendy and their son Danny, must live isolated from the rest of the world for the winter. But they aren't prepared for the madness that lurks within.","genre_ids":[27,53],"popularity":14.883,"vote_count":18628,"poster_path":"/uAR0AWqhQL1hQa69UDEbb2rE5Wx.jpg","release_date":"1980-05-23","vote_average":8.2,"backdrop_path":"/mmd1HnuvAzFc4iuVJcnBrhDNEKr.jpg","original_title":"The Shining","original_language":"en"},{"id":696,"adult":false,"title":"Manhattan","video":false,"overview":"Manhattan explores how the life of a middle-aged television writer dating a teenage girl is further complicated when he falls in love with his best friend's mistress.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":3.8199,"vote_count":2566,"poster_path":"/k4eT3EvfxW1L9Wmt04UqJqCvCR6.jpg","release_date":"1979-04-25","vote_average":7.718,"backdrop_path":"/adnSTomHU9YyqV2lx38CgM0UxLS.jpg","original_title":"Manhattan","original_language":"en"},{"id":702,"adult":false,"title":"A Streetcar Named Desire","video":false,"overview":"A disturbed, aging Southern belle moves in with her sister for solace — but being face-to-face with her brutish brother-in-law accelerates her downward spiral.","genre_ids":[18,53],"popularity":1.9191,"vote_count":1449,"poster_path":"/aicdlO5vt7z2ARm279eGzJeYCLQ.jpg","release_date":"1951-09-18","vote_average":7.619,"backdrop_path":"/or90vNrOVnYwi07fYYpQ3pbnjxP.jpg","original_title":"A Streetcar Named Desire","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt27431598","twitter_id":null,"f